  &lt;/profiles&gt;
&lt;/settings&gt;
```

This worked great, right through Maven version 3.8.4. But it does not work for any newer Maven 3.8.x versions or Maven 3.9.x. Note that it relies on the `my-sub-module` directory path in the `&lt;exists&gt;` element to make it somewhat specific to this project.

For older Maven, the following commands output the password as expected in both cases:

